longBusinessSummary: Bullion Gold Resources Corp. engages in the exploration, and development of mineral properties in Canada. The company explores for gold deposits. It owns interests in the Bousquet project, which consists of 71 claims covering an area of 2,370 hectares located in the Abitibi area in the province of Quebec; and Bodo SM lithium project covering an area of 36,420 hectares located in Canada. The company is based in Montreal, Canada.
